Day 36: Deploy Nginx Container on Application Server

Date: October 4, 2025
Overview
Deployed my first containerized web server using Nginx.
Key Concepts Learned

Docker run command
Port mapping
Container lifecycle
Image pulling from Docker Hub

Commands Used
bashdocker pull nginx
docker run -d -p 80:80 --name my-nginx nginx
docker ps
docker logs my-nginx
Challenges Faced
Port conflicts! Had to ensure port 80 wasn't already in use by another service.
